First Intuition to create collection of all allowed numbers.

# Approach
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
For allowed Numbers, created array of first n natural numbers, then replaced banned number with 0 and finally removed all zeros. Then iterated over array till we reach maxSum. And return the current index.

# Complexity
- Time complexity:
