# Code
```
class Solution {
    public int maxCount(int[] banned, int n, int maxSum) {
        HashSet<Integer> set = new HashSet<>();
        for(int i:banned)
        {
            set.add(i);
        }
        int sum = 0;
        int count = 0;
        for(int i=1;i<=n;i++)
        {
            if(!set.contains(i))
            {
                sum+=i;
                count++;
            }
            if(sum<=maxSum && i==n)
            {
                return count;
            }
            if(sum>maxSum && i!=n)
            {
                count--;
                sum-=i;
            }
            if(sum>maxSum && i==n)
            {
                return count-1;
            }
        }
        return count;
    }
}
```

